              <p>
                  These Terms and Conditions (the "Agreement"), contains all of the terms and conditions between Favo, Inc. ("Favo") and you as a Commercial
                  Provider (as defined below) and govern your participation in the Favo Commercial Provider Request for Information Program described herein
                  (the "RFI Program") offered on the Favo website and through any Favo mobile application (collectively, the "Site"). Please read this
