                  results and otherwise. Users have the ability, at their option, to request information about You or Your services via the method or methods
                  offered on the Site, which may include completing a request for information form on the Site, which Favo will then send an email to You,
                  calling You via a phone number posted on our Site provided the call lasts at least ten seconds, linking to Your Site via a website text
