                  request the credit within ten (10) business days of the date the of cancelation, using the process specified at enrollment, or otherwise
                  updated and communicated to You by Favo. Favo will investigate the request and will reply with the result of the credit request
                  investigation within five (5) business days of receiving the credit request. All Favo decisions are final. Favo reserves the right to
                  contact the User who submitted the optional service to assist it in determining whether the optional service is eligible for a credit
                  pursuant to the credit criteria listed above. Requests for credit that are approved by Favo generally will be credited against the
                  following month's charges. If the credit amount exceeds the following month's charges, the credit balance will be carried over to future
                  months until the full amount has been credited. If Your account is closed either by You or by Favo for any reason and a credit balance
                  remains, Favo will refund to You the remaining credit balance within thirty (30) days.
              </p>
